====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# A member of the [[class]] of [[animal]]s ''[[Aves]]'' in the [[phylum]] [[Chordata]], characterized by being warm-blooded, having [[feather]]s and [[wing]]s usually capable of [[flight]], and laying [[egg]]s.
#: ''Ducks and sparrows are '''birds'''.''
